title: Paal 69
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, International, Western, Juice bar, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Beach bar with many vegan dishes for breakfast, lunch, dinner and snacks. Serves fresh vegetable juices and offers coffee with soy milk for a small additional fee. Sandwiches can be made with gluten free bread. Menu also includes the dutch weed burger, a soy based vegan burger flavored with seaweed.
